results.story: The Sneakersnstuff x New Balance womens 991 Made in England Secret Colorway is inspired by the Swedish retailers first ever collaboration with New Balance: two 577 colorways developed in 2005 by SNS founders Peter and Erik. The latters design was color-adjusted following an initial batch of 96 pairs, which was released by SNS as a Secret Colorway. Modeled after that shoe, this pair combines a white leather base with contrasting overlays in mint green suede and yellow leather. The sneaker is finished with a two-tone ABZORB midsole.
